                   message.type === 'voice' ? '🎤 Voice note' :
                   message.type === 'location' ? '📍 Location' : '👤 Contact'}
                </Text>
                <Text style={[{ fontSize: 14 }, { color: isOutgoing ? appTheme.colors.textMuted : appTheme.colors.textSecondary }]}>
                  Not available in this version
